snippet.title: Amber Heard Told Her Mother Johnny Depp Was a 'Madman' Early in Their Relationship, Court Hears [New
snippet.description:
Advertisement    Amber Heard told her mother that her ex-husband Johnny Depp was “violent” and a “madman” during the course of their relationship, according to text messages read out to the British Court Thursday.   ...
